Subject: [PATCH 2/7] Add useful CLI tools to Docker image

Adds jq, ripgrep, fd-find, htop, tmux, vim, ffmpeg, imagemagick,
build-essential, python3-pip, sqlite3, and other tools useful for
AI agent operations.
---
 .github/workflows/docker-build.yml | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/.github/workflows/docker-build.yml b/.github/workflows/docker-build.yml
index 4f625f105..f7894f966 100644
--- a/.github/workflows/docker-build.yml
+++ b/.github/workflows/docker-build.yml
@@ -55,3 +55,5 @@ jobs:
           labels: ${{ steps.meta.outputs.labels }}
           cache-from: type=gha
           cache-to: type=gha,mode=max
+          build-args: |
+            CLAWDBOT_DOCKER_APT_PACKAGES=jq ripgrep fd-find tree htop ncdu tmux fzf vim nano netcat-openbsd dnsutils iputils-ping openssh-client rsync build-essential cmake python3-pip python3-venv sqlite3 pandoc imagemagick ffmpeg zip unzip p7zip-full xz-utils file less bc procps lsof strace man-db socat httpie postgresql-client redis-tools
